title: #92Noon! Bercich/Frangie/Florio/Brandt/Gleeman
description: Pete Bercich analyzing the Vikings to start the show, Jax voice Frank Frangie tells us about Yannick Ngakoue, Florio's weekly appearance, NFL Network's Kyle Brandt loves Kirk Cousins, and Gleeman is in for the final hour on the Twins!
